OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1774555873
OL,3,CHow is the conflict in Iran affecting
OL,4,CSomerset farmers?
OL,6,FA farmer from Somerset says he fears
OL,7,Fthe effects of extreme weather and
OL,8,Frising costs could make it
OL,9,Funsustainable for him to continue
OL,10,Ffarming.
OL,12,FEd Coombes, who runs a dairy farm near
OL,13,FLangport, said the hangover of storm
OL,14,Fflooding and the impact of the Middle
OL,15,FEast crisis on his costs mean his
OL,16,Foutgoings are set to rise by half this
OL,17,Fyear.
OL,19,F"It's a constant battle with
OL,20,Feverything really," he said.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
