OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1774555873
OL,3,CHow is the conflict in Iran affecting
OL,4,CSomerset farmers?
OL,6,F"Fuel's gone up - it is sky high at
OL,7,Fthe moment - fertiliser prices are up,
OL,8,Fseed prices are up. Everything's
OL,9,Fcreeping up."
OL,11,FParts of Somerset were devastated by
OL,12,Fflooding caused by Storm Chandra in
OL,13,FJanuary 2026.
OL,15,FIt took Mr Coombes' fields eight weeks
OL,16,Fto dry out, leaving behind dead grass
OL,17,Fand compacted soil.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
