OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1774555873
OL,3,CHow is the conflict in Iran affecting
OL,4,CSomerset farmers?
OL,6,FIt means he cannot let his 240 cows
OL,7,Fout to graze, and it will take months
OL,8,Fto re-sow and grow a fresh crop of
OL,9,Fgrass.
OL,11,F"You keep thinking to yourself, it
OL,12,Fcan't be that bad next year, next year
OL,13,Fwill be better," he said.
OL,15,F"But the reality is it doesn't seem to
OL,16,Fget much better."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
