FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1774555873
OL,3,CHow is the conflict in Iran affecting
OL,4,CSomerset farmers?
OL,6,FDespite producing more than 7,000
OL,7,Flitres of milk a day, Mr Coombes' farm
OL,8,Fis set to make a loss this year, and
OL,9,Fhe says the Government is "too far
OL,10,Fdetached from reality" to understand
OL,11,Fthe pressures facing farmers.
OL,13,FThe Government says it has raised
OL,14,Findustry concerns about diesel prices
OL,15,Fwith the Competition and Markets
OL,16,FAuthority and that it's committed to
OL,17,Fensuring the market functions fairly.
OL,19,FIt said it was ready to act swiftly to
OL,20,Fsupport the farming industry and
OL,21,Fprotect food security.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/4
